{
  "title": "Mildly Spicy Kenyan Chicken Stew",
  "description": "A floral and juicy Kenyan dish featuring oyster sauce, cooked in a clay pot and served on a bamboo tray, perfect for a sick day, this low-carb-friendly stew is a delicious and comforting meal.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
